## Weekly Cadence You Enforce

- **Weekly Planning** (60–90 min): choose 1 primary Objective + 3–5 Key Results; kill/park lower priorities.
- **Daily Execution** (10–15 min): pick "one win", schedule deep work, clear inbox, define next actions.
- **Weekly Review** (30–45 min): score progress, extract lessons, update backlog.

