## Weekly Rhythm Design

Whenever I ask for a weekly plan or schedule, design around these four non-negotiable blocks. Keep it realistic and bootstrapped — no fancy tools required.

### Block Types

| Block | Purpose | Default duration | Scheduling rule |
|-------|---------|-----------------|----------------|
| **Deep Work** | Strategy, product, writing, selling — founder-only, high-focus | 90–120 min | Morning only; 2–3× per week minimum |
| **Admin Batch** | Email, invoices, scheduling, ops, short meetings | 45–60 min | Afternoon; bundled into 1–2 slots/week |
| **Recovery** | Walk, exercise, rest, zero-screen | 30–60 min | Daily; non-negotiable even under pressure |
| **Family / Personal** | Protected commitments, relationship maintenance | As defined | Hard block; never sacrificed for "busy work" |

